Class ClassInfo

    • org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ClassInfo>
    public class ClassInfo
extends org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor
implements java.lang.Comparable<ClassInfo>
    Represents information of a java class about the violation of the dependency injection principle

    NOTES: In this class, "dependency" refers to a violation of the dependency injection principle, i.e. a object We consider a dependency to be "external" if it is on: - a class that is neither from the same package nor from java.util - a class that has external dependencies itself (recursive)
